{"word":"G2964 - κυρόω - kyróō - koo-ro'-o - Confirm","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κυρόω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">kyróō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">koo-ro'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Confirm</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - உறுதிபண்ணு, காண்பி"},{"paragraph":"to make valid; to confirm publicly or solemnly, to ratify"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the same as <a href=\"#/G2962 - κύριος - kýrios - koo'-ree-os/2962\">G2962</a>; to <i>make authoritative</i>, that is, <i>ratify:</i> - confirm.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G208/208\">G208</a>, <a href=\"#/G2964/2964\">G2964</a>"}]}